Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A new message from a supposedly dead Samu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us has opened it yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:12.12,Samu Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,1000)\fs70\pos(1064,495)\frz25.19\c&HEEFBFF&}Sumi no Koto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll die if we look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As if that would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't it a little scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe those kind of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in ghosts and the occult
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike before
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,50)}2 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,62)}Sorry, I think I got that last part wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I made a mistake too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure but I think I got it wrong too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot it too, right Samu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I'm sure I did well
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well what nothing we can do now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just do our best next time\N- Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone makes mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So no one blames anyone for it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, I've always thought about it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that we can laugh like this over such things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe its the reason why we're not selling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not looking anyway\N- Yeah, no one would notice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I never had an interest in fortune telling up 'till that point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an uneasy feeling at that time so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ambitions are quite strong
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there seems to be a "wall" obstructing your job that you need to bust through
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel that your friends are still immature
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and it kind of gets on your nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can {\i1}see{\i0} it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like she already knows everything about me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you'll have to look for a blue object
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it will let your efforts bear fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A blue object...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In today's ticket holders
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi's spot seemed to have a lot more people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:03:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just by chance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the sales recently, don't you think we're doing good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate maybe we can reach Budoukan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we come Budoukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How many thousands of people would fit there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it tens of thousands?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it should be 100,000
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After following my fortune, my luck has turned around
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,With luck quickly taking effect
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling it really is thanks to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But after all, our goal is Tokyo Dome right?\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you strive, things can really change
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you it has to be Budoukan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For your fortune telling needs, it's Nanahoshi Seira here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When I try looking at your fortune,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can kind of see something unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, I'd like for you to come see me again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A female evil spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,, I believe this evil spirit is preventing your success
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we try an exorcism?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Exorcism?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I got worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for the exorcism
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The exorcism costs 30,000
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? It's Hasumi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just deposited it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen carefully okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're getting the exorcism but
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there seems to be 2 evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:06:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For this instance, we will need a higher level of exorcism so
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless I don't call another exorcist of my level, I won't be able to deal with it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I did ask for it but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anymore money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's money then there are plenty of ways to get it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't your problem alone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Misfortune will befall even your family
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that fine with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,From then on I continued following her advice
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Following everything she said, I deposited the money
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the exorcism isn't enough to handle it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,looks like it would be good to get a guardian spirit to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare another 100,000
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the guardian spirit's spiritual power is too weak
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need to power it up even more so
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly deposit another 300,000
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have great luck
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The guardian spirit is amazed by you, and it would be great if you can give 1 million now to seal the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes....Okay, thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw the flyer and I'm calling to inquire...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're there right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Hasumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be troublesome if you don't pay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're there aren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it would be better to get out here quickly right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay up brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was driven into a corner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's my reason for living
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If the train were to get derailed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and just crush me, it would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In order for Samu to not find me out, I tried to regain my composure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Out on a walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me then if you're free
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It has become intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous so please clear off
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To the me who lives a useless life, watching pro wrestling,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why they are trying to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But watching them with so much energy in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel their drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I can feel my body fluttering with the excitement
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that you were a pro-wrestling fan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I like it though
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm opening it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls! There you are just standing come on let's drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it come on let's go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna read it in a more quiet place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Komiyama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It really has been!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You really came to visit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go back to Tokyo now though
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're done here, would you give us a ride back as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be taken away by a truck
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,without even noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The driver said she committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After buying stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As if
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, do you know what she bought?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Milk chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She bought a whole pack you know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,33 pieces inside
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,33?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was curious so I asked about it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 3 kinds of chocolate inside
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ah today's this flavor" she goes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She eats that happily everyday as if drawing fortune slips.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You think a person like that would commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a suicide after all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As if Samu would do something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is until here fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you very much\N- Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I heard about it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you're set to be in Budoukan right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations\N- Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how you guys {\i1}really{\i0} feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you guys actually feel upset and jealous, and that it can't be helped?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted it to be you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the ones I'm handling now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get there with you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad so I'll say this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Was it that it really wasn't meant to be you guys?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But the timing really just wasn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday for sure in another opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the perfect timing will come with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,May it be in work, or in love
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let the {\i1}Budoukan{\i0} then get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go up that same {\i1}stage{\i0} and {\i1}sing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll {\i1}sing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time, that you said something when we needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just Kimu's words of affirmation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you guys go there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's room 202
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,202?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:15:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's feels so nostalgic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't changed at all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's still the same
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my spot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is my spot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This was Samu's seat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,One-click phishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those malicious stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a phishing scare will stop us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Afforestation volunteer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this Samu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop global warming she said
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's save the endangered polar bears from the effects of global warming!" it says
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,White bears...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Udagawa {\i1}White Bears{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't today the day White Bears was formed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It is! I totally forgot about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably a scheduled message, I heard apps can do that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Samu remembered
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The day we were formed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we weren't just nothing to her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you guys been up to recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm living together with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My girlfriend, for that matter
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a lesbian, actually
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really happy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we have enough money, someday we're planning on starting a cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds nice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I am currently undergoing group therapies
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,People who can't stop drinking gather and talk about their experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kimu you don't drink..?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...that was a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you must've been holding back this entire time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job Kimu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now I'm working as Kirara's manager
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You two really get along well
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been keeping from everyone but
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In all honesty, I've always envied Kirara
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also done what haters do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For you to be her manager despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that's admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently an OL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.92,TL Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,52)}OL= Office Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,While working to pay my debts, I go watch pro-wrestling at the weekends
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's nothing to worry about anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You really worked hard
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:21.31,TL Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(635.2,51.2)}TN: Lyrics made with the help of translations found in stage48.net
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hane no Kioku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our debut song
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like this intro
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the lyrics too
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The costumes are super cute too
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see, the me 10 years in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you I wonder? What are you doing I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time, I wonder if I will be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would be nice to be with you, laughing together
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the usual road, where the sunlight passes through the trees
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That scenery alone will never change
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've thought about our future
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will our dreams come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will we not give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time, I hope the two of us are still friends
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Joking around together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would be great if our lives turn out that way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sky exists for us to soar, not just to look up to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought as I see the birds flying effortlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I can do now, with what is on my back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the memory of wings that I have not used, I have to believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In Samu's sudden death, it made us remember a lot of things
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But in a somewhat anticlimactic event with indifference,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,our daily lives continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:23:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever dies, whatever happens, everyday life will continue to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,without taking responsibility for your sadness; cruel, but unknowingly gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it's the exact reason why we continue living
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In the advent of the end of Samu's short life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it reminds us that there's still a long road ahead of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With this reality, though it brings tears to our eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,life won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.08,0:23:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Our almost dumb same as always everyday lives, as long as that is there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:41.89,Samu Title,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.96\fad(800,0)\pos(792,453)}Samu no Koto
